	<key>A management key can control your whole OpenRouter account, including creating and deleting other API keys. AgentMeter only reads usage and balance — it cannot spend credits or change anything. A regular API key is safer; use Connect to get a dedicated key for AgentMeter that you can revoke anytime.</key>
