	<key>This API key lets apps use your OpenRouter credits up to a spending limit you set. AgentMeter only reads how much has been used; it cannot spend money or change your account. If you used Connect, OpenRouter created a dedicated key just for AgentMeter that you can revoke anytime.</key>
	<string>Esta clave API permite que las apps usen tus créditos de OpenRouter hasta un límite de gasto que tú defines. AgentMeter solo lee cuánto se ha usado; no puede gastar dinero ni cambiar tu cuenta. Si usaste Conectar, OpenRouter creó una clave dedicada solo para AgentMeter que puedes revocar en cualquier momento.</string>
	<key>This API key lets apps use your OpenRouter credits. AgentMeter only reads usage; it cannot spend money or change your account. If you used Connect, OpenRouter created a dedicated key just for AgentMeter that you can revoke anytime.</key>
